<section id="Creating_a_Domain" remap="TID_41994">
	<title>Creating a Domain</title>
	<procedure>
		<title>To Create a Domain</title>
		<step>
			<para>
				Navigate to <menuchoice><guimenu>Automate</guimenu><guisubmenu>Explorer</guisubmenu></menuchoice>. The default view is the Datastore.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/1847.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject><guilabel>(Configuration)</guilabel>, then 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/2365.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> <guilabel>(Add a New Domain)</guilabel>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Type in a unique <guilabel>Name</guilabel> and <guilabel>Description</guilabel>. Choose if the Domain is <guilabel>Enabled</guilabel>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click <guilabel>Add</guilabel>.
			</para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
	<formalpara>
		<title>Result:</title>
		<para>
			The new domain is created.
		</para>
	</formalpara>
</section>